__DESCRIPTION__

I've been having more fun, and doing more perl side projects since I started playing with Questhub.

In this talk I'll cover:

* What is [Questhub](http://questhub.io/)?
* How do you use it?
* How do I use it?
* Why you might want to give it a go.
